translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_18e02859:
    # "Unable to get to sleep, Sarah had taken to wandering the camp."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_7039065c:
    # "All around the lake that she had drawn from the earth, there were now small improvised encampments."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_8f372495:
    # "In a few, a campfire still burned, in others, only the embers were left."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_b5147edc:
    # "Here and there, Sarah could hear the murmurs of festivities drawing to an end. Here and there, the sounds of bodies connecting."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_4fefb977:
    # "Sarah ignored it all, weaving through the darkness between the camps."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_d1eed5ae:
    # "She wanted to be alone for a while."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_5748f6e7:
    # "Alone with her own thoughts."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_bba5c2b7:
    # "Though the soldiers of the mercenary company had taken the lake for the miracle that it was, and had thrown plenty of praise on her, Sarah still struggled with it."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_0f262dcb:
    # "The voice that had moved her to strike the earth and draw forth the water..."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_24376f8e:
    # "How could such a thing be."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_c36371b8:
    # "Slowly, Sarah made her way up the flank of one of the dunes."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_7be30cbe:
    # "From the elevated position, she could look out across the camp and its few remaining lights."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_7d774fa6:
    # "Turning around in the other direction, Sarah saw the stretching desert, reaching all the way to the horizon."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_ba49297e:
    # "A gust of wind rushed past her, across her naked body, the cold taking root in her."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_9231d839:
    # "She oddly welcomed the cold."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_c5e4d6a8:
    # "Behind her, the camp was quiet. Gone was the simmering resentment that had hung over them like a cloud."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_5a0757b4:
    # "Sarah drew in a deep breath, taking in the desert air."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_46d8b2ad:
    # "Looking out across the vast space, she imagined that it looked little different from the desert at any other point since leaving Bagrad."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_dc320b7d:
    # "If not for the pain in her muscles and the sores on her feet, she could have imagined that they had barely moved at all."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_95ac04bb:
    # "A darkness stood out."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_3cdbba68:
    # "For a moment, in the moonlit night of the desert, it had appeared as an oddity, but slowly Sarah felt her eyes drawn to it."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_20985131:
    # "A darkness that was more like a void, filled with starlight"
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_90a27706:
    # "Black as ink."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_c1480993:
    # "The more she looked, the more Sarah felt herself drawn to it, and in turn, the greater it appeared to be and become."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_24b56f1f:
    # "Rising."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_ddb36129:
    # "From the emptiness of the desert, a pitch-black emptiness began to rise."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_c6bf48fa:
    # "Sarah could feel her breath, catching in her throat as the thing contiued to grow, rising up far above the horizon."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_362acf28:
    # "Soon, the thing pierced the sky itself, contrasted against the backdrop of the world."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_d14ef693:
    # "Sarah felt a jolt in her body."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_61ec4f70:
    # "And the world resumed itself."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_d47b0aa4:
    # "As sudden as the pillar had appeared, so instantly had it vanished."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_848d6beb:
    # "And the world was back as it had been, except, now the absence of the void appeared in itself to be odd. As if the natural world was itself now lacking something."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_03c066c5:
    # "Sarah raised up her hands to her breasts and felt herself breathing, her chest rising and falling."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_524a9cf7:
    # "She knew she was awake."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_a54db22a:
    # "She knew the thing had been real."
    ""

translate ru oasisresolvelabel1_37419b76:
    # "And Sarah knew, though she could not say how, where the city of Nauyziri rested."
    ""

